{"tid":2419109,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(G)I-DLE穗珍又爆「連演員也霸凌」譏：沒父母笨蛋　徐信愛IG暗諷","createTime":"2021-02-23T06:01:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T08:14:55.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a777108d906f55deed94e2e77564c1ad5caa41ba","tid":2419109,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T06:01:55.000Z","msg":"南韓女團(G)I-DLE成員穗珍日前被爆校園霸凌，連22歲女演員徐信愛都疑似是受害者之一。對此，她否認霸凌徐信愛，並表示「在學校的時期，從來沒跟她說過話」，並向被牽連到這件事情的徐信愛道歉。怎料，在穗珍全盤否認後，徐信愛持續在Instagram發出若有所指的動態，「你不是我朋友，不要裝作懂我的心情。」穗珍再度陷入霸凌風波。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5466/d5466960.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5466%2Fd5466960.jpg&h=ff77657c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲(G)I-DLE穗珍與徐信愛就讀同一所國中，但她否認霸凌對方，並表示「學生時期從沒跟她對話過」。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據網友過往的爆料中，「我還記得徐某哭著跟我說，上學的路上，在那位朋友身後喊著她『笨蛋，妳沒父母該怎麼辦才好』，每天扯著嗓子大聲喊，但是妳（穗珍）出演節目時，還有臉笑著說跟她讀同個學校，真是雞皮疙瘩掉滿地。」文章內所說的徐某被挖出就是22歲女演員徐信愛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5466/d5466962.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5466%2Fd5466962.jpg&h=bd526201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲徐信愛過去數度透露自己是校園霸凌受害者「電視劇裡演得霸凌都是真的」。（圖／翻攝自韓網）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不僅如此，徐信愛過去數度坦言「電視劇裡演得霸凌都是真的」、「曾經在很會玩的朋友面前被傷得滿身瘡痍」，這段過去的發文此時再被掀出，令不少人更確信關於穗珍爆料文中被提及的徐某就是在講徐信愛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5466/d5466961.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5466%2Fd5466961.jpg&h=33dd65e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲(G)I-DLE穗珍否認霸凌後，徐信愛IG又若有所指地發文「不要裝作懂我的心情」。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n關於徐信愛的相關爆料，(G)I-DLE成員穗珍否認，並表示「在學校的時期，從來沒跟她說過話」，然而，穗珍否認沒多久後，徐信愛在IG動態貼出怪奇比莉的歌曲《Therefore I am》，歌詞暗指「你不是我朋友，不要裝作懂我的心情。」此文貼出後，在韓引起熱烈議論，就徐信愛第二篇貼出的動態，(G)I-DLE成員穗珍所屬公司Cube娛樂還未有回應。"},{"pid":"85d49d2989b0820b13a14622ab48802357231e56","tid":2419109,"uid":255310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T06:02:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba7d2502bf358583418985c896fec3a1639ff875","tid":2419109,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T06:05:23.000Z","msg":"打靶女<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"828b7583a4598919544f5728db6cd6cfcede82bc","tid":2419109,"uid":52073,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T06:26:09.000Z","msg":"斬殺"},{"pid":"8cf658c70ffaecbbd4d200a2cb2eb08ae9a5e156","tid":2419109,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"828b7583a4598919544f5728db6cd6cfcede82bc","tid":2419109,"uid":52073,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T06:26:09.000Z","msg":"斬殺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T06:28:42.000Z","msg":"狗頭鍘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bdea7129c6cc86beaa4f7f9ae4d5b212818508c","tid":2419109,"uid":141656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T06:30:39.000Z","msg":"molamola <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f431a89fc141c84708f9d5495377adfbe1d03f1","tid":2419109,"uid":294121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T06:31:47.000Z","msg":"咁樣衰恰得少"},{"pid":"75ff4df8cb355eff34ab28245050b91a579d9adf","tid":2419109,"uid":384534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T06:34:18.000Z","msg":"怪奇比莉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"013dbdc960b6a9966017a6ca742ea6f528028fb6","tid":2419109,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T06:52:05.000Z","msg":"壞女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /